IPL different Season Winners¶

In [50]:
season = matches['season'].unique()
def winnerOfIPL(year):
    winner = []
    for i in year:
       winner.append(matches[matches['season']==i][-1:]['winner'].values[0])
    return winner
winner = winnerOfIPL(season)
